    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Đáp án: 36"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      250,
      1636,
      1186,
      1730
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "+ Ta có $b^3 - \\frac{3b-1}{4} = \\frac{4b^3 - 3b + 1}{4} = \\frac{(2b-1)^2(b+1)}{4} \\ge 0 \\Rightarrow \\frac{3b-1}{4} \\le b^3$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      250,
      1739,
      958,
      1827
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vì $a < 1$ nên $4 \\log_a \\left( \\frac{3b-1}{4} \\right) \\ge 4 \\log_a (b^3) = 12 \\log_a b$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      250,
      1841,
      1130,
      1933
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "+ Ta có $c^2 - \\left( \\frac{c}{2} - \\frac{1}{16} \\right) = c^2 - \\frac{c}{2} + \\frac{1}{16} = \\left( c - \\frac{1}{4} \\right)^2 \\ge 0 \\Rightarrow \\frac{c}{2} - \\frac{1}{16} \\le c^2$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      250,
      1946,
      945,
      2033
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vì $b < 1$ nên $3 \\log_b \\left( \\frac{c}{2} - \\frac{1}{16} \\right) \\ge 3 \\log_b (c^2) = 6 \\log_b c$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
